snippet: The police in Anchorage are investigating reports of a “verbal and physical altercation” at the party last weekend.
abstract: Alaskan police are investigating whether members of Sarah Palin's family participated in a brawl during a birthday party in Anchorage; Palin, in a Facebook post, says that she had been traveling the day the party was held.

byline.original: By AMANDA COYNE and LIZETTE ALVAREZ
byline.contributor: Amanda Coyne reported from Anchorage, and Lizette Alvarez from Miami.

lead_paragraph: The police in Anchorage are investigating reports of a “verbal and physical altercation” at the party last weekend.

headline.main: Palins Said to Be Involved in Brawl at Party in Alaska
headline.print_headline: Palins Said to Be Involved in Brawl at Party in Alaska
